{"tid":1605680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位夢遊者","createTime":"2019-09-30T11:01:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T11:30:54.000Z","uid":100467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d83c689b660811f64857624d39d1ea9f94103e04","tid":1605680,"uid":100467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:01:14.000Z","msg":"今朝好多TG手足比人拉左<br />\n而夜晚放工時間相信狗仔會繼續咬人<br />\n如果大家係屋企附近見到一啲可疑人物<br />\n大約三至到四個<br />\n而佢望住你嘅時候有一種敵視嘅眼神<br />\n心口袋放左電話同時鏡頭對撚住你嘅話<br />\n唔該大家小心啲<br />\n比啲警覺性<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15221affc44e7dfe63137e220907b476dae44b86","tid":1605680,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:02:00.000Z","msg":"Telegram 預設訊息可以保護到手足性命<br />\n希望大家可以幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCXiwqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCXiwqP.png&h=5c04cb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星火 TG: @Abccbbc<br />\n612 TG: @ReliefFund612<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"bb3ab213caedb0fe63eea703f8b5420c4eff08ce","tid":1605680,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HrcFMoG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHrcFMoG.jpg&h=5701f015&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T8u1vQo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT8u1vQo.jpg&h=f4dbbed9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d8a391134b38f901f91431a900e0a97d5441e51","tid":1605680,"uid":100467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:05:36.000Z","msg":"狗仔今晚至明天早上應該會繼續咬人，各位感覺自己好惹狗的手足請注意以下幾點：<br />\n<br />\n1. 狗仔如果選擇夜晚收工時間上門咬人，大概徘徊19:00 - 22:00期間，留意時間；<br />\n<br />\n2. 如果選擇哩個時間段上門，多數會在手足屋企附近(尤其屋企樓下)擺咗狗仔隊等待獵物出現，緊記狗仔隊一定唔會似狗樣，唔好唸住見唔到有外貌似狗隻人士就覺得自己安全，以下為狗仔隊特徵：<br />\nA.) 穿著簡單，甚至踢拖，完全唔似出街look；<br />\nB.) 對眼一定會望你，因為你係佢獵物；<br />\nC.) 最明顯特徵：中意將手機插落胸口袋，鏡頭向外，鏡頭方向同佢目光方向一致，因為同緊上頭FaceTime緊<br />\n<br />\n3. 如果狗仔隊就在你身邊，佢會特登做某些動作，消除你疑慮，例如扮同隔離個人傾計<br />\n<br />\n如果發現有狗仔隊出現，即刻九秒九轉身走人，千祁唔好翻屋企住，因為佢就係等緊你返屋企上門拉你兼搜屋<br />\n應該立即離開去安全地方，最好立即飛的，有咁遠走咁遠"},{"pid":"f9c2abfde51ba969d006ad8f6af7e6bb36c8e2fa","tid":1605680,"uid":150267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:30:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">三點燒黨旗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">［主線］<span style=\"color: red;\">聽日一定要做啲有標誌性嘅</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1604870\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1604870</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武 和理非入<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\"> 依到有合集帶啲咩</span></strong><br />\n［整合］<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一執齊野</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603888</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">無豬咀就帶定條濕毛巾cover 口同鼻 <br />\n會好啲</span><br />\n<br />\n同埋唔好行甘前</span><br />\n<br />\n仲有巴打目標post<br />\n十一國殤　六區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1600404\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1600404</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}